keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Node

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Node.Node
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NodeAssert, NodeConsequent, NodeExprArit, NodeExprHold, NodeLabel, NodeRule, NodeRuleBase

    public abstract class Node
extends java.lang.Object

    The class defines the characteristics of a node. Every variable has the same linguistic labels and does not use weights. Terminal nodes have the same own attributes and haven't got pointer to children. Internal nodes only have got pointer to children.

    Since:
    JDK1.5

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Written by Luciano Sánchez (University of Oviedo) 20/01/2004, Modified by M.R. Suárez (University of Oviedo) 18/12/2008, Modified by Enrique A. de la Cal (University of Oviedo) 21/12/2008
